➤ Fully playable DELTARUNE hypotheticals, running on your everyday home computer!

This is a DELTARUNE fangame featuring a collection of hypothetical scenarios, each imagined as a fully playable segment of gameplay. Discover the hidden mysteries that connect these scenarios as you dive into each one, unraveling an existential truth about you and every adventure you’ve been on so far.
